OL,3,CRiot prisoner 'strange' after arrest,
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FA custody sergeant has told an inquest
OL,7,Fthat "with hindsight" a prisoner
OL,8,Farrested following a riot outside an
OL,9,Fasylum seekers' hotel should have been
OL,10,Freferred to mental health workers.
OL,12,FPeter Lynch, 61, was found dead in his
OL,13,Fcell at HMP Moorland in South
OL,14,FYorkshire on 19 October 2024, two
OL,15,Fmonths after he was given a two-year
OL,16,Fsentence for his part in disorder
OL,17,Foutside the Holiday Inn Express in
OL,18,FRotherham.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
