PN,33802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784809124
OL,3,CRiot prisoner 'strange' after arrest,
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FA jury at Doncaster Coroner's Court
OL,7,Fwas told on Monday he behaved
OL,8,Fstrangely after he was arrested on 10
OL,9,FAugust and refused to talk to police.
OL,11,FIn evidence, Sgt Ryan Handley agreed
OL,12,Fthat he had made a note of how Mr
OL,13,FLynch's presentation had been
OL,14,F"strange" in the custody suite at
OL,15,FShepcote Lane Police Station, in
OL,16,FSheffield, and that he had been
OL,17,Fconfused.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784809124
OL,3,CRiot prisoner 'strange' after arrest,
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FSgt Handley said Mr Lynch would not
OL,7,Fgive his surname to officers, and
OL,8,Fanswered every question put to him by
OL,9,Fsaying he was "Peter, living man, son
OL,10,Fof Michael and Lily".
OL,12,FThe officer said the prisoner also
OL,13,Frefused all offers of food and drink
OL,14,Fwhile he was on duty.
OL,16,FAsked by Doncaster's senior coroner,
OL,17,FNicola Mundy, if he spotted any "red
OL,18,Fflags" in Mr Lynch's presentation, Sgt
OL,19,FHandley said he did not.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@TO]yD@aOUzD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784809124
OL,3,CRiot prisoner 'strange' after arrest,
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FThe officer was asked by Richard
OL,7,FCopnall, representing Mr Lynch's
OL,8,Ffamily, whether it would have been
OL,9,F"sensible" to involve the liaison and
OL,10,Fdiversion team, who deal with mental
OL,11,Fhealth issues among detainees.
OL,13,FSgt Handley said: "With hindsight,
OL,14,Fyes."
OL,16,FBut the officer did not agree with Mr
OL,17,FCopnall that he should have deemed Mr
OL,18,FLynch unfit for interview.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]uD@SOUvD@EO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784809124
OL,3,CRiot prisoner 'strange' after arrest,
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FHe said: "I'm going to stick with my
OL,7,Fassessment that he was fit to be
OL,8,Finterviewed at that time."
OL,10,FSgt Handley said Mr Lynch was seen by
OL,11,Fthe healthcare team in relation to the
OL,12,Fmedication he brought with him to the
OL,13,Fpolice station, but not in relation to
OL,14,Fhis mental health.
OL,26,@nD@JOUpD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784809124
OL,3,CRiot prisoner 'strange' after arrest,
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FHe confirmed that there was no
OL,7,Frequirement for him to refer to
OL,8,Fhealthcare professionals in deciding
OL,9,Fwhether a prisoner was fit to be
OL,10,Finterviewed, saying he made that
OL,11,Fdecision 10 to 20 times a day in
OL,12,Frelation to people in custody.
OL,14,FEarlier, histopathologist Laszlo
OL,15,FKarsai told the jury that Mr Lynch
OL,16,Fdied by hanging at least two to three
OL,17,Fhours before he was discovered.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784809124
OL,3,CRiot prisoner 'strange' after arrest,
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FThe pathologist said there were traces
OL,7,Fof medication in Mr Lynch's body
OL,8,Fcompatible with his known medical
OL,9,Fhistory of heart disease and diabetes,
OL,10,Fbut these conditions did not
OL,11,Fcontribute to his death.
OL,13,FThe coroner read a statement from
OL,14,Fanother police officer which described
OL,15,Fhow a flag was found in Mr Lynch's
OL,16,Fhouse "that could be be linked to far
OL,17,Fright ideology".
OL,19,FThe inquest continues.
OL,26,@xD@GOUyD@OO]
